RELATIONS:
- TYPE: Parent
  VALUE: GHOST-MEM-REC-FILE-DELETE-VALIDATE

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: GHOST-MEM-REC-FILE-DELETE-REPORT
STATUS: Draft
TITLE: Delete History Report
STATEMENT: >>>
The delete result shall report file identity, prior filenames, title, and number of vectors deleted when available.
<<<
RELATIONS:
- TYPE: Parent
  VALUE: GHOST-MEM-REC-FILE-DELETE-VALIDATE

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: GHOST-MEM-REC-UI-DELETE-CONFIRM
STATUS: Draft
TITLE: Typed Delete Confirmation
STATEMENT: >>>
The current Streamlit file action shall require the exact trimmed text delete before confirming history deletion.
